# Lumon QOL priorities

When improving this repo, prefer the roadmap in [`.cursor/plans/lumon-qol-p0-p4.plan.md`](.cursor/plans/lumon-qol-p0-p4.plan.md):

- **P0**: Reliable CRT pointer open, one-click kiosk/fullscreen, arm-length idle HUD
- **P1**: Phone thumb habit UX, desk-as-portal, install naming
- **P2**: Richer rare ambient (not more frequent), discoverability hint, cam chyron
- **P3**: Geometry visuals, focus traps/dialogs, self-hosted fonts
- **P4**: Pointer-path Playwright smoke, `npm start`, ambient session report, SW bump docs

Product defaults: secondary-monitor ambient first; rare ambient stays hours-scale; habit protocols stay; vanilla ES modules.
